root.title: 5 Best Pick-up Line Comebacks
root.content: Man – Haven’t I seen you someplace before? Woman – Yes, that’s why I don’t go there anymore. Man – Can I buy you a drink? Woman – I think I’d rather have the money! Man – Will you go out with me this Saturday? Woman – Sorry, I’m having a headache this weekend. Man – Is this seat empty? Woman – Yes, and this one will be if you sit down. Man – So what do you do for a living? Woman – I’m a female impersonator.
